## ðŸ–¼ Flow (ASCII Diagram)

```
+--------------------------+
| Malicious IOC Confirmed  |
+--------------------------+
            |
            v
+--------------------------+
| XSOAR Playbook Trigger   |
| (IOC = "High Risk")      |
+--------------------------+
            |
            v
+--------------------------+
| Push to Firewall (PAN-OS)|
+--------------------------+
            |
            v
+--------------------------+
